Well, at least you’re leaving
me conscious this time around.

273
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:07,460
Sorry, I have to go.

274
00:19:07,860 --> 00:19:09,460
We’ll chill some other time.

275
00:19:09,650 --> 00:19:10,570
You need a ride?

276
00:19:11,690 --> 00:19:13,620
No I think I’ll just
hang here for a bit.

277
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,390
Cool.

278
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:17,200
Go, go, go play footsie or
whatever it is you do.

279
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:21,490
Oh, and I forgot,

280
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:23,940
I’m out of hash.
Can you give me some?

281
00:19:31,100 --> 00:19:33,610
Think I’m out as well, sorry.

282
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,940
Shit. Okay, so...

283
00:19:36,330 --> 00:19:37,140
...ask Mishra.

284
00:19:37,950 --> 00:19:39,070
Yeah I’ll do that.

285
00:19:39,250 --> 00:19:40,600
If I can find him that is.

286
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,310
Okay, bye.

287
00:19:45,130 --> 00:19:45,660
Maggie!

288
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:46,460
Yeah?

289
00:19:47,990 --> 00:19:49,900
Nothing, nothing…
See you!

290
00:19:50,830 --> 00:19:51,630
Bye.

291
00:19:55,876 --> 00:19:57,876
