and save the world after this?

1129
01:24:31,080 --> 01:24:31,890
Anyhow...

1130
01:24:32,911 --> 01:24:35,221
Thupten says they need
all the help that they can get.

1131
01:24:35,940 --> 01:24:38,170
Marie Sartre is there;
she is covering the protest and...

1132
01:24:38,445 --> 01:24:41,005
Since our road trip has come
to this untimely end.

1133
01:24:44,604 --> 01:24:45,524
We should go.

1134
01:24:45,990 --> 01:24:48,110
We should help in
whatever way we can.

1135
01:24:50,895 --> 01:24:52,055
Sounds boring.

1136
01:24:55,368 --> 01:24:58,118
But after all we’ve been through,

1137
01:24:59,416 --> 01:25:01,146
I think boring is
exactly what I need.

1138
01:25:03,812 --> 01:25:05,042
Let’s go!

1139
01:25:28,971 --> 01:25:31,831
We are burning embers in a
world of deepening shadow...

1140
01:25:33,482 --> 01:25:35,612
...and the road we tread on has no end.

1141
01:25:38,276 --> 01:25:40,046
But there is still the sky,

1142
01:25:41,021 --> 01:25:44,391
the windy mountain and
the river below it.

1143
01:25:47,894 --> 01:25:48,884
So let’s tread on,

1144
01:25:50,427 --> 01:25:53,037
