peaks of our dying kingdom.

1145
01:25:53,842 --> 01:25:55,182
For there is still the sky,

1146
01:25:55,978 --> 01:25:57,408
the windy mountain,

1147
01:25:57,910 --> 01:25:59,460
and the river below it.

1148
