of our age old values!

1350
01:39:39,602 --> 01:39:42,112
An insult to our Gandhian ways.

1351
01:39:42,838 --> 01:39:46,208
The people of these
hills, they are victims.

1352
01:39:47,115 --> 01:39:50,835
